    <content>&lt;P&gt;I tried adding the 'Cost Center' Pre-Condition in Wokflow for Parked Invoice as Complete and it worked.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="JesseJSilaen_0-1710398362768.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/80406i97F33C765992D850/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="JesseJSilaen_0-1710398362768.png" alt="JesseJSilaen_0-1710398362768.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Then now I try to make a selection from 'Cost Center' which is like search help but when I apply ddic_type 'KOSTL' Search help cost center doesn't appear&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="JesseJSilaen_3-1710398465517.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/80409i56A78308565D07ED/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="JesseJSilaen_3-1710398465517.png" alt="JesseJSilaen_3-1710398465517.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;but when I change ddic_type to BUKRS the search help appears.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="JesseJSilaen_1-1710398398647.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/80407i9A2B5D94A4B4F747/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="JesseJSilaen_1-1710398398647.png" alt="JesseJSilaen_1-1710398398647.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="JesseJSilaen_2-1710398424230.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/80408i2DFD68D4B997E8DE/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="JesseJSilaen_2-1710398424230.png" alt="JesseJSilaen_2-1710398424230.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&