    <content>&lt;P&gt;I am Trying to create a custom situation handling scenario where a notification will be triggered after every FG Goods movement, it will help the Logistic team to plan dispatch activities.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;For this purpose I have created a custom situation object using Event Object "&lt;SPAN&gt;CL_MMIM_MATDOC_EVENT" i.e Material Document Created. And further created Situation Scenario and Type Accordingly. When I run the Situation type using batch trigger i get the appropriate notification&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Ashish_Talekar_1-1710513448040.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/81507iF6EC69DB90C388B9/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Ashish_Talekar_1-1710513448040.png" alt="Ashish_Talekar_1-1710513448040.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Ashish_Talekar_2-1710513479809.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/81508i18F29D07AE42CCA7/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Ashish_Talekar_2-1710513479809.png" alt="Ashish_Talekar_2-1710513479809.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;But when triggering an Event I get the following Error "Message =Data loss occurred when converting 20244900000941" it is unable to separate Document Year and Number.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Ashish_Talekar_0-1710513405304.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/81506i145BA1CB9EF2720C/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Ashish_Talekar_0-1710513405304.png" alt="Ashish_Talekar_0-1710513405304.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thanks &amp;amp; Regards&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Ashish Talekar&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/Situation+Handling/pd-p/db4786c7-74ce-4e4a-91f2-027a57fa3921" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="253-1"&gt;Situation Handling&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/SAP+S%25252F4HANA+Public+Cloud/pd-p/08e2a51b-1ce5-4367-8b33-4ae7e8b702e0" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="1199-1"&gt;SAP S/4HANA Public Cloud&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/3332"&gt;@Saumitra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
